{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"他好像至死也不相信你能杀了他。","tone":"无奈","chapter":29,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"就因为他不信，所以他才会死。","tone":"淡然","chapter":29,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"有些事的确是一个人至死也不会明白的……","tone":"无奈","chapter":29,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"多尔甲","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"布达拉","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"晚上你自己从不点灯？","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"为什么要点灯？","tone":"疑问","chapter":29,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"不点灯我也一样可以看得很清楚。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":30,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"我看不清楚。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":32,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"你随时都可以走，我并没有留你。","tone":"淡然","chapter":29,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"可是你也没有赶我走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"我不必。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"不必？","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"该走的时候，你总是要走的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":42,"line_en