{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"明天他真的会来？","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"当然会来，他并不知道多尔甲已是个死人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":204,"line_end":204},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"血书通常只有两种意思。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":210,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"哪两种？","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"一种是临危时的绝笔，一种是表示情况的危急严重。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"魔教中人写血书，通常都不是用自己的血。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":220,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"你认为这封信是真的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":222,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"绝对不假。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"你怎么能确定？","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":226,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"这就是你的晚饭？","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":240,"line_end":240},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"两个人吃？还有谁要来？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":29,"line_start":246,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"没有别人了，我一向很少请客。","tone":"淡然","chapter":29,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"现在你只有一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":29,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"你不是人？"